">节省 $16.50</span> </div></div><div class="flex w-full flex-col flex-nowrap justify-center gap-2 text-black no-underline md:order-2 md:gap-y-6"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-y-2 md:w-full md:gap-y-1"><div class="block w-fit cursor-pointer font-akshar text-lg font-medium leading-5 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-xl md:leading-6"> Dreo Falcon S 智能风扇</div></div><div class="hidden md:flex md:justify-between md:gap-x-4"><div class="w-full mb-0 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>84.99 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$99.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $15.00</span></div></div> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm hidden self-end h-12 max-w-[10rem] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:bg-brand-green-700 md:flex md:h-10">获得优惠</button></div></div><div class="flex aspect-video h-[90px] shrink-0 items-center justify-center self-center md:order-1"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/02i4scfnSUvkWppA7Oel6RO/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1707297123.jpg" alt="Dreo Falcon S 智能风扇" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm w-full h-12 duration-200 ease-in-out hover:bg-brand-green-700 md:hidden md:h-10">获得优惠</button><div class="flex flex-col items-center w-full md:hidden font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>84.99 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$99.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $15.00</span></div></div> <button class="mb-4 mt-6 pr-4 font-akshar text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 hover:cursor-pointer hover:text-brand-green md:pr-8" x-cloak x-show="!showMore &amp;&amp; 6 >; 3" x-on:click="showMore = !showMore" x-on:keydown.enter.prevent.stop="showMore = !showMore">查看更多 3 个</button><use href="https://lifehacker.com/images/icons/spritemap.svg#sprite-chevron-right"></use></div><p>但这还不是最好的部分。所有 Dreo 风扇（台式、立式、塔式和吊扇）都有一个标记为“自然”的设置，它会每隔一段时间改变风扇的功率，以模拟室外微风的感觉<em>，而且它很有效。</em>我的 Dreo 风扇安装在各处房子：我的厨房里有一个台式风扇（厨房里应该一直有一个风扇）；我的卧室里有一个立式风扇，今年我的空调使用量减少了很多；还有一个吊扇；最新添加的是我的鸡舍的风扇，当温度过高时它会自动启动。<br><br>这些粉丝之一可能不会是您在 Prime Day 购买的最大金额，但它可能是最能改善您生活的粉丝。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/tech/these-dreo-smart-fans-are-on-sale-for-prime-day<dc:creator>阿曼达·布鲁姆</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Hardware]]></category></item><item><title>这款 Brava 智能台面烤箱 Prime Day 立减 400 美元</title><guid ispermalink="false">01J2W2WBYDQG5F5V5HEYR155C6</guid><pubDate> Tue, 16 Jul 2024 11:15:00 +0000</pubDate><description>台面烤箱效果非常好，它合理地激发了我更频繁地做饭。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01J2W2WBYDQG5F5V5HEYR155C6/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>我确实喜欢做饭，但我也很忙、很累，而且众所周知，我经常从 Grubhub 订购。然而，在过去的六个月里，我一直在使用 Brava Glass 智能烤箱（目前 Prime Day 折扣 400 美元），它让在家做饭变得不再那么麻烦。</p><p> Brava Glass 是一款智能台面炉，其占地面积与大型烤箱相同，但它使用一系列灯管以惊人的速度烹饪所有东西，而且几乎完全不需要动手。您只需通过触摸屏查找您想要烹饪的食物，然后选择您的食谱。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> Brava 玻璃智能烤箱</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>1,595.00 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$1,995.00</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $400.00</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">获得优惠</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/029fxYOGs3tY5vjelkmKWhd/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1721077554.jpg" alt="Brava Glass：10 合 1 触摸屏台面智能烤箱、玻璃门、无线温度计、空气炸锅、6 片烤面包机、慢炖锅、再加热器、脱水机、电饭锅、自动关闭、1800W" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/029fxYOGs3tY5vjelkmKWhd/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1721077554.jpg" alt="Brava Glass：10 合 1 触摸屏台面智能烤箱、玻璃门、无线温度计、空气炸锅、6 片烤面包机、慢炖锅、再加热器、脱水机、电饭锅、自动关闭、1800W" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">获得优惠</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>1,595.00 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$1,995.00</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $400.00</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>有两个温度探头（有线和无线），您可以使用其中任何一个，但在许多情况下根本不必使用它们。烤箱配有一系列金属托盘、玻璃托盘、鸡蛋托盘，甚至还有一个非常漂亮的陶器砂锅，所有这些都可以在烤箱中使用。触摸屏将指导您完成所有步骤，包括使用哪个托盘、将其放在顶部还是底部，以及如何插入温度探头（如果需要）。打开烤箱后，您可以通过手机上的应用程序观看食物烹饪的视频。</p><p>烤箱可以处理一切。如果您需要翻转食物，烤箱会停止，通知您并等待您这样做。食物完成后，烤箱就会关闭。更奇怪的是，由于烹饪方式的原因，烤箱的外部根本不热。</p><p>如果您在触摸屏上找不到正确的食谱，您可以简单地设置烤箱的温度和时间，然后像使用其他烤箱一样使用它。光的工作方式使这一切变得如此快速和有效——烤土豆在 10 分钟内就变成了完美的棕色。任何蛋白质都完全煮熟，外面烤焦，里面嫩。没有比这更简单的方法来烤蔬菜或做馅饼了。我用它的主要目的是将蛋白质和蔬菜放在托盘上，用盐、胡椒和橄榄油调味，然后让烤箱来处理。它只需要付出最少的努力，同时确保取得令人难以置信的高水平的成功。</p><p> Brava Glass 在 Prime Day 优惠 400 美元，虽然对于台面烤箱来说价格昂贵，但如果它能帮助你减少点外卖的频率——我认为它会的——那么数学就解决了。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/food-drink/brava-glass-smart-oven-prime-day<dc:creator>阿曼达·布鲁姆</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Food & Drinks]]></category></item><item><title>我最喜欢的扫地机器人在 Prime 会员日享受历史最低价格</title><guid ispermalink="false">01J2VP8TNH8TDMAJHGHBSVP9HK</guid><pubDate> Tue, 16 Jul 2024 11:00:00 +0000</pubDate><description>这款地板机器人非常适合小型家庭、办公室或公寓。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01J2VP8TNH8TDMAJHGHBSVP9HK/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>大多数扫地机器人的尺寸并不是很大，但<a href="https://lifehacker.com/tech/switchbot-k10-plus-robot-vacuum-review" target="_blank">Switchbot K10+ 的</a>尺寸约为标准地板机器人的一半。它就像在你的地板上跑来的小巧克力豆，但这个尺寸发挥了它的优势——这就是为什么它是我在较小空间的首选，也是<a href="https://lifehacker.com/tech/four-features-to-look-for-in-a-robot-vacuum-and-one-that-doesnt-matter" target="_blank">为什么我今年每次写关于机器人吸尘器的文章时都会提到它</a>。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> SwitchBot 迷你扫地机器人 K10+，自清底座可清洁 70 天，激光雷达导航，扫地机器人和拖把组合，可定制清洁，48 分贝超静音，最长 150 分钟，与 Alexa 兼容</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>299.99 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$399.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $100.00</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">获得优惠</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/02e2HgseRkp2FbJH41JW8Pc/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1721070999.jpg" alt="SwitchBot 迷你扫地机器人 K10+，自清底座可清洁 70 天，激光雷达导航，扫地机器人和拖把组合，可定制清洁，48 分贝超静音，最长 150 分钟，与 Alexa 兼容" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/02e2HgseRkp2FbJH41JW8P